data.description: Welcome to this incredible 5-bedroom home nestled in Krislynn Woods subdivision,where the community spirit thrives!Situated on almost an acre of land, this property offers a serene setting with a stunning wooded landscape.The play possibilities are endless with neighborhood playground & gaming courts, allows all a chance to be & enjoy the outdoors!As you step inside you'll be greeted by the warm & cozy atmosphere that instantly makes you feel at home. The spacious living areas are perfect for gatherings.The kitchen has been recently remodeled & is a cook's dream!Plenty of cabinets and counterspace. Options to eat at the breakfast opening or in the formal dining room.Everyone can have their own tranquil retreat within their own large bedroom space. The primary bedroom boasts a large en-suite bath that makes your daily routine a breeze. Another gem of this space is the large pool that awaits your vision for those upcoming hot summer days!A lot is offered here for the price+Home Warranty!
